y I hate doing major raiding with 3 or more groups and being in an &quot;uber&quot; guild.<br><br>1) I hate being a friggin number to people.<br><br>2) If you cant spell my name properly why should I buff you... &quot;NOW&quot;<br><br>3) Why In gods green earth should I be the one to tash the damn dragon as a guest, die a five or ten times and get nothing for my troubles?<br><br>4) Let me restate that, why would any chanter want to go to ntov and die five or ten times to get a bunch of melees more crap.<br><br>5) I'm a firm believer in the fact that other then a couple of flowing thought items, that I really don't need any more gear when my resists are 100  and cha/int is over 225. Its not like casters get that many cool looking robes.<br><br>6) At least have the decency to talk to your chanter during a raid about anything other then the next piece of friggin armor you hope drops because 9 times out of 10 we really don't give a rats ass cause we aren't going to see crap coming our way.<br><br>7) Get a friggin clue, we go from being necessary in all content outside of &quot;uber&quot; mobs and unless those mobs can CH then there is really no reason to have more then one chanter who looks at the screen ever 30minutes or so, haste all the tanks, cast kei, maybe a gmr and walk away for awhile.... oh wait its called bored off my ass.<br><br><!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Anyone else think that zerging a mob is the most boring way to kill a mob(thank god for mana burn)?<br><br>9) Anyone else in your guild think to try to make a chanter for the guild? Oh wait, they don't want to actually WORK on a character that is almost impossible to power level unless they are babysat for every waking second.<br><br>10) When was the last time you role played, I'm finding its a whole lot more fun to play with druids(very polite when they want kei), ogres(self explanatory) and wizards(how hard is it role play getting your kicks off blasting cute furry animals into oblivion) in that order.<br><br>11) Anyone else in the world actually like to dungeon crawl rather then camped named mobs all day long?<br><br>12) Aoe groups are a lot more fun at times because even a halfway decent monk makes the game to trivialized now days.<br><br>Um... cant think of more but I'm sure if zehn gets a whole of this, he could think of a few. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/usirtaino.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SirTainO</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elder</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(7/2/02 7:52:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1621.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What is it with chanters and guilds</span><hr size=1> Yes, the Legend is looking for chanters.<br>Yes, I see why you are no guild material at all.<br><br><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Sig deleted – too big. Rules are: 150 high, 450 wide, no greater than 50kb. –Nark</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/unark84.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nark84</A> at: 7/2/02 6:38:55 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uanterakayonaero.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AnterakAyonaeRo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Local Resident</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(7/2/02 8:24:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1621.topic&index